    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced with a plate kit, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. The suspension features an upgraded coilover setup for improved damping and roll center adjustment. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are superb, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that remains the benchmark for the segment.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
