    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been garage-kept and serves as a testament to responsible ownership. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the black leather sport seats show minimal bolster wear and remain soft to the touch; all cabin electronics, including the PCM infotainment and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is turn-key. It features a complete service history with the most recent major interval completed recently, including a fresh oil service and brake fluid flush. The turbocharged engine pulls cleanly through the rev range, paired with a crisp-shifting manual transmission that provides an engaging driving experience. The tires offer plenty of tread for the seasons ahead, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is an honest, well-cared-for example ready for its next enthusiast owner who values mechanical integrity and a classic aesthetic.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
